(firstQuint)Salvage: Postconditioning With Adenosine for STEMI.

 Prospective, single center, randomized clinical study.

 Study design is random patient assignment to selective intracoronary administration of adenosine or control immediately before restoration of coronary artery patency in patients presenting with an acute ST segment-elevation myocardial infarction (STEMI).

 Randomisation will be stratified for the duration of symptoms ( 4 hours).

